########################################
Key files and scripts for the
LAMMPS workshop ethanol example
########################################

generate_datafile.py
--------------------

This script will create a new LAMMPS configuration
of ethanol using the OPLS force field.

in.mol_npt, in.mol_nvt
----------------------

These are the LAMMPS input files that you
will need.


plot-npt.py
-------------

This script will plot the density as a function of time for the NPT run
and compare with the experimental value at 298K

plot-nvt.py
-------------

This script will plot the pressure as a function of time for the NVT run


pylat.sh
----------

This shell script invokes PyLAT for the NVT LAMMPS trajectory
and computes the self-diffusivity and RDF. It places everything
in a json file.


plot-pylat.py
-----------------
This script plots the MSD and RDF of the json
file created by PyLAT



